data.text: Friday, June 21, 2024, Philadelphia, PA I would like to thank God Almighty for allowing this event to take place without incident. A lot of questions were answered, a lot of connections were made and there's more to come. Our first Community Conversations to discuss solutions for gun violence in the city of Philadelphia was held this past Friday. Thank you @iam_sheeeeeed for providing us with your vision. I would like to thank my partners @the_coachali @kfc6323 @twallace45 @g2msports @moodynwatsonllc #melissa.
